: Question about WToV vs HoT drop rate</span><hr size=1> Considering two leather tunics dropped on a Lendi kill (just clearning the trash around her), a BP dropped on the way up to Telk (Factioning is fun here) and a tunic dropped on the way to Gozz I would have to say drops are much better in WToV - too bad we didnt do West when we were farming armor.  We didnt discover the great drop rate until we started to farm ST keys and cleared the mobs around Lendi the first time.<br>
<br>
However its a little more difficult than HoT due to getting there.   In HoT you likely are on CoV and dont have to worry about CoH.  In West you are ruining your CoV every kill and need Kael anyway to do the turn ins.<br>
<br>
